Kh2 f6 27. Bh6 Rf7 28. Qg4 {The position is still complicated, but Black is
not losing immediately. The pin over the g7-square is extremely annoying, but
Black has an active queen and material advantage.}) 25. Bh6 Rf7 26. Qg5 f4 27.
Rg4 1-0

